#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tango is a Canada-based software company focused on building modern, scalable digital products by combining cutting-edge technology with AI-assisted development. We help organizations move faster, build smarter, and deliver higher-quality software without unnecessary complexity."
msgstr "Tango 是一家总部位于加拿大的软件公司,专注于将前沿技术与 AI 辅助开发结合,构建现代化、可扩展的数字产品。我们帮助组织更快前进、更聪明地构建,并在没有不必要复杂度的前提下交付更高质量的软件。"

