#: lib/kanban_web/controllers/page_html/tango.html.heex:83
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "We saw possibilities not just for startups, but for development teams of any size—across private and public sectors, and in virtually any industry."
msgstr "我们看到的可能性不仅针对初创公司,也面向任何规模的开发团队——跨私营与公共部门,几乎覆盖所有行业。"

#: lib/kanban_web/controllers/page_html/tango.html.heex:78
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "What began as an internal learning journey—exploring the real-world potential of AI-assisted development—quickly became something more. As we experienced the impact firsthand, we realized how powerful it is to put AI directly into the hands of experienced engineers. The results reshaped how we think about software delivery."
msgstr "最初这是一段内部学习旅程——探索 AI 辅助开发的现实潜力——很快便演变为更深远的事物。在亲身体验其影响后,我们意识到将 AI 直接交到经验丰富的工程师手中是多么强大。结果重新塑造了我们对软件交付的认知。"

#: lib/kanban_web/controllers/page_html/tango.html.heex:149
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Whether you're exploring AI-assisted development, modernizing existing systems, or building something entirely new, we partner closely with your team to turn ideas into high-quality, production-ready solutions. Our approach blends experienced engineers with AI-powered workflows to deliver results faster, with greater accuracy and long-term maintainability."
msgstr "无论您是在探索 AI 辅助开发、现代化现有系统,还是构建全新事物,我们都会与您的团队紧密协作,将想法变成高质量、可上线的解决方案。我们的方法结合经验丰富的工程师与 AI 驱动的工作流,以更快的速度、更高的准确性和长期可维护性交付成果。"

#: lib/kanban_web/controllers/page_html/tango.html.heex:88
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "While many large organizations attempt to improve outcomes by measuring productivity, our experience shows that true gains come from"
