#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Stride is an AI-native work management system. Humans plan, review, and approve. Agents claim, build, and ship. Same board. One workflow. No glue code."
msgstr "Stride 是一款 AI 原生的工作管理系统。人类负责规划、评审、批准。Agent 负责认领、构建、交付。同一块看板。一套工作流。没有胶水代码。"

